[sitemap]
cont_site = '<p>The sitemap page provides an overview of all available links on the website. These include the Seed Shop, the CBD &amp; Terpene Shop, the Growshop, the Headshop and various blog posts on different topics relating to cannabis cultivation. In our seed store you will find a large selection of Cannabis seeds, divided into CBD-rich varieties, feminized seeds, THC-rich varieties, autoflowering seeds and medicinal seeds.</p>
<p>In the CBD &amp; Terpenes Shop we offer you a variety of CBD products such as flowers, oil, drops and more, as well as terpenes and other products made from Cannabis. The Growshop has everything you need for growing cannabis, from lighting technology, fertilizers and substrates to ventilation and climate control. In the Headshop you will find bongs, grinders and other smoking accessories. Our blog posts provide you with interesting information and tips on cannabis cultivation.</p>'
heading_tag_content = 'Popular search queries'

