text_checkout = 'Below you will find the order form for manually ordering your products. Please tick the desired payment method and shipping option and complete the missing details. Print out the order and send it to us. We recommend that you do not enclose any small change, hide the cash in an extra envelope, folded paper, postcard or between two cardboard boxes and send the letter sealed with extra adhesive tape by registered mail! <br>  <br> Bank details and DHL Packstation... <br> '
